						<p class="auSubHeader">Compliance and Liability</p>
						<p class="auTextBlock">This AUP is intended to protect You, us, our other customers, and the Services and Internet community in general from improper, inappropriate, abusive, or illegal activity. When using the Services, You are required to comply with this AUP and are expected to adhere to commonly accepted practices of the Internet community. The prohibited uses described below are intended as guidelines regarding improper and inappropriate conduct, and should not be interpreted as an exhaustive list.</p>
